tournament.name: New-Bee KQSF 2-23-23
tournament.description:
$2 entry per person
Thurs. Feb 23, 2023

BYOT or as a free agent

A Killer Queen tournament for the masses! 

Bring a team or sign up as a free agent and we will help form teams. 

Love Killer Queen, but feel like the regulars are too good for you to play in a tournament? This Killer Queen tournament is designed for you! KQSF league veterans who have been playing for more than 6 months are BANNED from entering* (sorry, not sorry).

Format of the tournament will be decided day-of to fully utilize our available time. (Four or fewer teams = double round robin into single elimination. 5-7 teams = round robin into single elimination or glory match. 8+ teams = Double Elimination). 

*If you don't know whether or not you qualify, please reach out to Brian Lee [Kato's Dad] to confirm. 

Disclaimer:
We plan to stream the event on Twitch with cameras. If you have concerns, please reach out to Brian Lee [Kato's Dad].
